What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Melamine Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Melamine Market

Melamine market will grow at a rate of 3.49% for the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Rise in the levels of growth associated with the construction industry acts as a vital factor driving the growth of melamine market.

Melamine is defined as a type of chemical compound that finds its application in a number of industrial and consumer goods & services. These organic compounds are utilized in the production of various laminates, dinnerware, coatings, flame retardants, adhesives and various others. It is characterized as having a white crystalline form.

Rise in the levels of demand from the automotive industry is the vital factor escalating the market growth, also rise in the growth of demand from wood adhesives and laminates application and increase in the levels of disposable income and changes in preferences and lifestyles of consumers are the major factors among others driving the melamine market. Moreover, rise in the research and development activities and increase in the demand from emerging economies will further create new opportunities for the melamine market in the forecast period of 2021- 2028.

However, rise in the concern amongst users regarding the emissions of melamine in moulding applications and rise in the presence of various substitute compounds and materials for different applications of melamine is the major factor among others acting as a restraint, and will further challenge the growth of melamine market in the forecast period mentioned above.

